Symbol.Script_1D:
eps = 0.00001
dim stStyles[5] stStyles[1] = `Стиль 1` stStyles[2] = `Стиль 2` stStyles[3] = `Стиль 3` stStyles[4] = `Стиль 4` stStyles[5] = `Стиль 5`
dim stTypeTextRotation[] stTypeTextRotation[1] = `Читаемый` stTypeTextRotation[2] = `Выровнять по Символу`
Symbol.Script_VL:
values "a" range (0, ) values "b" range (0, ) values "fsp" range (0, ) values "fsz" range (0, )
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "A" then parameters b = a if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "B" then parameters a = b lock "B"
! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Styles ! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- values "stStyle" stStyles values "iStyle" 1, 2, 3, 4, 5
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "stStyle" then iStyle = 1 if stStyle = stStyles[2] then iStyle = 2 if stStyle = stStyles[3] then iStyle = 3 if stStyle = stStyles[4] then iStyle = 4 if stStyle = stStyles[5] then iStyle = 5 parameters iStyle = iStyle else stStyle = stStyles[1] if iStyle = 2 then stStyle = stStyles[2] if iStyle = 3 then stStyle = stStyles[3] if iStyle = 4 then stStyle = stStyles[4] if iStyle = 5 then stStyle = stStyles[5] parameters stStyle = stStyle endif
! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Pen limitations ! -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
parameters fpen = fpen parameters dnpen = dnpen parameters snpen=snpen parameters dlpen = dlpen parameters cpn = cpn
if fpen <= 0 then parameters fpen = 1 if dnpen <= 0 then parameters dnpen = 1 if snpen <= 0 then parameters snpen = 1 if dlpen <= 0 then parameters dlpen = 1 if cpn = 0 then parameters cpn = 1
if iStyle = 1 then hideparameter "upper", "bCalcUpper", "lower", "bCalcLower", "right", "bCalcRight", "left", "bCalcLeft" endif if iStyle = 2 then hideparameter "upper", "bCalcUpper", "lower", "bCalcLower", "right", "bCalcRight", "left", "bCalcLeft" hideparameter "fsp" hideparameter "iNumUpper", "iNumRight", "iNumLower", "iNumLeft" else hideparameter "bUpper", "bRight", "bLower", "bLeft" endif if iStyle = 3 then hideparameter "upper", "bCalcUpper", "lower", "bCalcLower", "right", "bCalcRight", "left", "bCalcLeft" hideparameter "txtElevationDef", "txtSheetDef", "tf", "fsp", "snpen" endif if iStyle = 4 then hideparameter "iNumUpper", "iNumLower", "iNumRight", "iNumLeft" endif if iStyle = 5 or iStyle = 5 then hideparameter "iNumUpper", "iNumLower", "iNumRight", "iNumLeft" hideparameter "txtElevationDef", "txtSheetDef", "tf", "fsp" endif
! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Fonts ! -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
parameters gs_FontSize= abs(gs_FontSize) values "gs_FontSize" range (0,]
parameters fsp= abs(fsp) values "fsp" range (0,]
parameters fsz= abs(fsz) values "fsz" range (0,]
! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Text Rotation ! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- values "typeTextRotation" stTypeTextRotation values "typeTextRotation_m" 2, 0
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "typeTextRotation" then typeTextRotation_m = 2 if typeTextRotation = stTypeTextRotation[2] then typeTextRotation_m = 0 parameters typeTextRotation_m = typeTextRotation_m else typeTextRotation = stTypeTextRotation[1] if typeTextRotation_m = 0 then typeTextRotation = stTypeTextRotation[2] parameters typeTextRotation = typeTextRotation endif
! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! UI ! -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
values "gs_ui_current_page" 1
Symbol.Script_UI:
ui_current_page gs_ui_current_page
TABID_ROOT = -1 TABID_GENERAL = 1
if TABID_GENERAL > 0 then ui_page TABID_GENERAL, TABID_ROOT, `Параметры Интерьерной Развертки`, "uiTab_Style_flat(1)" gosub "generalPage" endif
! ============================================================================= end ! =============================================================================
"generalPage": pageStartY = 5
ui_infield{3} "iStyle", 0, pageStartY, 444, 260, 1, 1, 5, 1, 105, 105, 85, 85, 1, stStyles[1], 1, 2, stStyles[2], 2, 3, stStyles[3], 3, 4, stStyles[4], 4, 5, stStyles[5], 5 return
Symbol.Comment: 2D-заголовок маркера интерьерной развертки с дополнительным текстом.
